text: Chromiec is a village in the administrative district of Gmina Stara Kamienica, within Jelenia Góra County, Lower Silesian Voivodeship, in south-western Poland. It lies approximately south-west of Stara Kamienica, west of Jelenia Góra, and west of the regional capital Wrocław. ==References== Chromiec
